# üé® Professional Portfolio Website

A modern, responsive, and high-performance portfolio website built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This portfolio serves as both an interactive CV and professional resume showcase.

![Portfolio Preview](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Live-success)
![HTML5](https://img.shields.io/badge/HTML5-E34F26?style=flat&logo=html5&logoColor=white)
![CSS3](https://img.shields.io/badge/CSS3-1572B6?style=flat&logo=css3&logoColor=white)
![JavaScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/JavaScript-F7DF1E?style=flat&logo=javascript&logoColor=black)

## ‚ú® Features

### üöÄ Core Features
- **Fully Responsive Design** - Works seamlessly on mobile, tablet, and desktop
- **Single File Solution** - Everything in one HTML file for easy deployment
- **Fast Loading** - Optimized images and efficient code (loads in < 1 second)
- **Smooth Animations** - Beautiful scroll-triggered animations and transitions
- **CV Download** - One-click downloadable resume/CV
- **Contact Form** - Functional contact form with validation

### üéØ Sections
- **Hero Section** - Eye-catching introduction with animated statistics
- **About** - Personal introduction and highlights
- **Experience** - Professional timeline with detailed work history
- **Skills** - Animated skill bars showing proficiency levels
- **Projects** - Showcase of featured work with images and links
- **Contact** - Multiple contact methods and form

### ‚ö° Performance Features
- Lazy loading images
- Optimized assets (600x400px, 80% quality)
- CSS animations using GPU acceleration
- Throttled scroll events
- Intersection Observer for efficient animations
- Fast initial load (0.8s loading screen)

### üé® Design Features
- Modern gradient backgrounds with parallax effects
- Professional color scheme (customizable)
- Elegant typography (Crimson Pro + DM Sans)
- Smooth hover effects and micro-interactions
- Animated "Available for Opportunities" badge
- Mobile-friendly hamburger menu

