## üöÄ Quick Start

### Option 1: Direct Use
1. Download `portfolio.html`
2. Open in any modern web browser
3. Done! ‚ú®

### Option 2: GitHub Pages
1. Fork this repository
2. Go to Settings ‚Üí Pages
3. Select `main` branch as source
4. Your site will be live at `https://yourusername.github.io/repository-name`

### Option 3: Local Development
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/portfolio.git

# Navigate to directory
cd portfolio

# Open with live server (or just open the HTML file)
# Using Python
python -m http.server 8000

# Using Node.js http-server
npx http-server

# Using PHP
php -S localhost:8000
```

## üé® Customization

### 1. Personal Information

Update the hero section with your details:
```html
<h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="title-line">Your Name</span>
    <span class="title-line title-highlight">Your Title</span>
</h1>
<p class="hero-subtitle">Your tagline or description</p>
```

### 2. Change Colors

Modify CSS variables in the `<style>` section:
```css
:root {
    --color-primary: #2d3748;      /* Main color */
    --color-accent: #d69e2e;       /* Accent color */
    --color-text: #1a202c;         /* Text color */
    /* Add your custom colors */
}
```

### 3. Update Projects

Replace project content in the Projects section:
```html
<div class="project-card" data-animate>
    <div class="project-image">
        <img src="your-image.jpg" alt="Project Name" class="project-img" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <div class="project-content">
        <h3 class="project-title">Your Project Name</h3>
        <p class="project-description">Your project description</p>
        <!-- Update tags and links -->
    </div>
</div>
```

### 4. Add Your Own Images

Replace Unsplash URLs with your images:
```html
<!-- Option 1: Local images -->
<img src="images/project1.jpg" alt="Project" class="project-img">

<!-- Option 2: Your own URLs -->
<img src="https://yourwebsite.com/image.jpg" alt="Project" class="project-img">
```

### 5. Update Experience & Skills

Edit the timeline and skills sections with your own experience and expertise.

### 6. Modify Loading Time

Change loading screen duration:
```javascript
const CONFIG = {
    loadDelay: 800,  // Change this value (in milliseconds)
    // Or set to 0 to remove loading screen
};
```

## üì± Responsive Breakpoints

